  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p558474/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201312/b55a70627fe748c0aac3149bc4bfc332.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tJustin Bieber handed a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bitter\" target=\"_blank\">bitter</a> Christmas present to millions of Beliebers. Just before midnight on Christmas Eve (Dec. 24), the singer tweeted that he was &ldquo;officially retiring.&rdquo;<span class=\"web-item\">贾斯汀&middot;比伯</span>给无数的比伯粉儿们送了一份苦涩的圣诞礼物。就在平安夜的半夜，这位歌手在推特上宣布他要&ldquo;正式退休&rdquo;。</p>\n<p>\n\tHowever, Bieber calmed the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/nerve\" target=\"_blank\">nerves</a> of his nearly 48-million followers about 40 minutes later, saying that he was &quot;here forever.&quot;但是，比伯在40分钟后又发文安抚他4800万粉丝，说他&ldquo;永远在这里&rdquo;。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201312/51415e631d2047508844e9c216d5e6b3.gif\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThe media talks a lot about me.They make a up a lot of lies and want me to fail but I'm never leaving you, being a belieber is a lifestyle.&mdash; Justin Bieber (@justinbieber) December 25 2013媒体们经常讲到我，他们编造了很多谎言想让我失败，但是我永远不会离开你们，这是比伯粉儿的生活方式。&mdash;&mdash;贾斯汀<span class=\"web-item\">&middot;</span>比伯2013年12月25日</p>\n<p>\n\tBe kind loving to each other, forgive each other as god forgave us through Christ Merry Christmas IM HERE FOREVER&mdash; Justin Bieber (@justinbieber) December 25 2013彼此之间友爱相处，彼此原谅，上帝通过基督原谅我们，圣诞快乐，我永远不离开。&mdash;贾斯汀<span class=\"web-item\">&middot;</span>比伯 2013年12月25日</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201312/51415e631d2047508844e9c216d5e6b3.gif\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201312/237ec9453d1047e1bcfac5e4a14cb5bc.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tJustin Bieber's 'Journals' Collection to Drop in Time for Chistmas.贾斯汀<span class=\"web-item\">&middot;</span>比伯的新专辑《Journals》在圣诞节期间放出。</p>\n<p>\n\tThe theme of Bieber's retirement popped up -- and was dismissed -- last week, when the singer told radio station Power 106 FM that his next album would be his last. 比伯退休的言论在上周就出现了，他在接受无线之声106FM采访时称，下张专辑将是他的最后一张。</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;The new album&hellip; I&rsquo;m actually retiring,&quot; he said. &quot;I&rsquo;m just gonna take some time. I think I&rsquo;m probably going to quit music.&quot; Scooter Braun, his longtime manager, quickly defused the bomb saying that Bieber was &quot;just kidding&quot; and was &quot;taking a break just to make music and relax, take some time for himself for the first time since he was 12.&quot;&ldquo;新专辑&hellip;其实我要退休了，&rdquo;他说。&ldquo;我需要时间休息下，我想我可能要退出音乐界了。&rdquo;消息发出后，比伯的经纪人斯科特<span class=\"web-item\">&middot;</span>布劳恩马上回应说比伯只是&ldquo;开玩笑&rdquo;，而且&ldquo;休息只是为了做音乐，放松，自他12岁以来第一次能好好休息一下。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\tWhether Bieber will actually hang up his mic for good, only time will tell. But the timing of his announcement will undoubtedly give the singer a bit of extra publicity, just in time for the release of his new movie, &quot;Believe,&quot; which opened worldwide on Christmas Day.至于比伯是否真的会收起麦克风，只有时间能告诉我们答案，但是，宣布隐退绝对会给这位歌手即将于圣诞节上映的传记电影《Believe》一点额外宣传。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p558474/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p558474\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p557963/\">麦当劳自己拆台：建议员工少吃快餐</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p557581/\">穿越时空的圣诞：亡妻留给丈夫的催泪礼物</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p552646/\">长得漂亮就够了：人越好看收入越高</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujia